headline: Freeport-McMoRan: Indonesian Reliance Creates A Complicated Investment Case
summary: Freeport-McMoRan's stock is highly tied to volatile copper prices and faces significant political risks from its operations in Indonesia. Read why FCX stock is a Hold.
